collection.description:

To those who live with their heads in the clouds: welcome home. The World of Boki is home to anyone and everyone.

Sidus NFT Heroes
collection.description:
SIDUS NFT Heroes is the original NFT collection featured in the SIDUS HEROES metaverse. The collection includes 6,000 generative characters created by NFT STARS and the international collective of modern artists NFT256.

The SIDUS NFT Heroes collection serves as an entry ticket to the SIDUS HEROES metaverse. You can lock your card on the SIDUS HEROES website and immediately receive a Hero, which will be released inside the game. Depending on the rarity of the Original NFT Hero, you will receive a Common, Epic or Legendary Hero in the game. 
After the lock period is over, you will get your card back and you can lock it again, if you wish, for another period and receive a new Hero inside the game.

collection.description:
[ Ledger ] Market is the most secure platform for artists and brands to release their NFTs, where Ledger customers can securely connect through Ledger Live and clear sign their transactions. For first access to exclusive collaborations, and Ledger hardware, software and services, become a [ Ledger ] Market Pass holder.


[ L ] Market’s brand mark is a generative font with over two billion unique variations. It speaks to: 1) the massive awareness generative art and PFP projects have brought to blockchain technology, and 2) the advanced cryptography built into Ledger and [ Ledger ] Market’s DNA.

EightBit Me
collection.description:
[EightBit](https://www.eightbit.me) is a collection of 8,888 NFT’s that are generated by countless 8-bit themed traits. Within the collection, there are rare outfits, items, and more surprises.

Each NFT contains a PFP and a full Digital EightBit Character which are stored on IPFS. All characters have their own page ([see example](https://www.eightbit.me/bit/7030)) that will become more interactive in time.

Back in 2010, we launched the original 8-bit avatar creator. Before a world of punks and apes, our app let you make a virtual 8-bit version of yourself. Check out it out in action [here](https://vimeo.com/20713468).

detail.name: VeeCon 2022 #2489
detail.description:
VeeCon 2022 - Created By Snowfro and Gary Vaynerchuk.

This token is a verifiable ticket for admission to VeeCon 2022, which is a multi-day event exclusively created for VeeFriends & the Web3 community.

Time: May 19th - May 22nd, 2022

Location: U.S. Bank Stadium in Minneapolis, MN, USA

To be admitted to VeeCon 2022, attendees must hold this token in a mobile-compatible NFT wallet and register it for admission with the official VeeCon event app. The VeeCon event and ticket registration app will be released in May 2022 on iOS and Android and will be used for verifiable ownership of this NFT, event registration, and programming.

To commemorate the first ever VeeCon conference, VeeFriends is honored to collaborate with Web 3 pioneer Erick 'Snowfro' Calderon. Snowfro, the founder of Art Blocks, a first of its kind generative blockchain platform, and creator of the Chromie Squiggle, collaborated on this collection during early Spring 2022 with Gary Vaynerchuk, the creator and visionary behind VeeFriends. Snowfro's squiqqles and Gary's doodles have melded together to create the artwork for the first NFT ticketed conference and to live forever on the ethereum blockchain.

If you plan to attend VeeCon 2022 with this ticket NFT please RSVP now at [VeeCon.co/RSVP](https://veecon.co/rsvp)

Instructions for how to use this ticket to gain admission to VeeCon are coming soon to [VeeCon.co](https://veecon.co/)!

Mavia Land
collection.description: Heroes of Mavia is a play-to-earn MMO Strategy game developed by Skrice Studios. The game takes place in a fantasy-themed island called Mavia, where players build bases on plots of land and battle neighboring bases and armies to earn in-game resources, such as Mavia’s P2E cryptocurrency RUBY. Players must strategically place defensive buildings on their base such as walls, turrets and traps, in order to defend against opportunistic attackers looking to steal resources. Resources can also be stolen from rival bases through attacking opponents with land troops, vehicle and air units. RUBY is earned through battling enemy armies, and can be used to upgrade Land, Statue and Hero NFTs.

detail.name: COMMON #960
detail.description:
Land is the most valuable NFT asset type inside of the Mavia ecosystem. Land is required in order to build a base, train an army and attack rival bases in order to earn Gold, Oil and RUBY. Your Land NFT can be used to play the game, but can also be used to form a partnership with another player, or can simply be rented out to others for passive RUBY income via the Mavia marketplace.

All land types behave the same in the game, and there is no offensive or defensive advantage to having higher rarity base. Common Land is the most frequently found base type, and it makes up 70% of the land in Mavia. Common Land has the least amount of environment decorations, the most basic type of map location and also has no extra luck factor when removing obstacles.

CryptoMories
collection.description:
"memento mori" means " remember you die" in latin. 
It is an old saying used to remind people that life is short, and must be lived to the fullest.
It is very often symbolized by a skull.
CryptoMories are 10 000 little skeletons here to remind you that life is good, that there are a lot of amazingly kind people, and that you are one of them. Focus on your greatness.

CryptoMories are not a basic 10k generative series. They are an adaptative generative series. 
One item differs from one Mori to another, depending on the type. A top hat on a zombie will have holes in it. This makes different types even more special. And it is extremely fun to try to figure out what item looks like on other types.

Also, there are many little fun games and easter eggs. Including VERY special Mories.. some might say unique..

CryptoMories are the second series of the iwwon project, after the Los Samos handmade one. Both can be combine to access the handmade series vandals. See more on discord.

Damien Hirst - The Currency
collection.description:
HENI is delighted to present The Currency, the first NFT collection by Damien Hirst. 

Starting with the creation of the physical artworks in 2016, The Currency explores the boundaries of art and currency—when art changes and becomes a currency, and when currency becomes art.

Collectors had 1 year to decide between the digital NFT or the physical artwork, both of which are artworks in their own right. Whichever was picked, the other got burned.

After the Exchange deadline, on 27th July 2022, the final NFT Supply is 4,851 NFTs. 5,149 NFTs were burned in exchange for the physical artworks. 

The collection was launched on the Palm blockchain, which is a token-powered ecosystem for NFTs connected to Ethereum. It is 99% more energy efficient than proof of work systems such as Ethereum or Bitcoin. The Currency NFTs can be moved to Ethereum using the Palm NFT Bridge.

The entire collection can be viewed by visiting https://currency.nft.heni.com/
